high_descs: Turn around and head towards the toilet.
Pick up the cardboard roll on the toilet basin.
Turn left towards the bathroom vanity on your right.
Open the bottom drawer that is second to right side and place the cardboard roll in the cabinet; close the door.
Turn right and walk towards the toilet on your left.
Pick up the toilet paper on the toilet basin.
Turn left towards the bathroom vanity on your right.
Open the bottom drawer that is second to right side and place the toilet paper roll in the cabinet; close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place the toilet paper and cardboard roll into the bathroom vanity.

high_descs: Cross the room to the toilet.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll that is on top of the toilet.
Move to the sink that is on the right.
Open the bottom cabinet drawer and place the roll inside.  Close the drawer.
Move back to the toilet that is on the right.
Pick up the full roll of toilet paper that is on top of the toilet.
Open the bottom drawer that is in the cabinet under the sink.
Place the full roll of tissue in the drawer. Close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put away the toilet paper rolls.

high_descs: walk over and face the front of the toilet
pick up the yellow tube off the top of the toilet
walk over to the bathroom sink
open the pull out drawer below the sink and put the yellow tube in it
walk back over to the front of the toilet
pick up a toilet paper roll off the top of the toilet
walk over to the sink again
place the toilet paper roll inside the same drawer
anns.task_desc: put a yellow tube with a toilet paper roll inside pull out drawer beneath the sink
